1. *Njega* je odveo u bolnicu. (He was taken to the hospital.)
2. Ona je za *njega* izabrala belu košulju. (She chose a white shirt for him.)
3. Ona je sve što *njega* čini srećnim. (She is all that makes him happy.)
4. On je imao puno pitanja za *njega*. (He had a lot of questions for him.)
5. *Njega* su smatrali za sveca. (He was considered a saint.)
6. *Njega* je većina ljudi poštovala. (Most people respected him.)
7. *Njega* su učili od malih nogu. (He was taught from a young age.)
8. Svi su se divili *njegovom* uspehu. (Everyone admired his success.)